content: No, I think I'm good. I wasn't saying I didn't like the emojis or anything, just observing that it was new, and we've gone through a lot of exciting moments together, so was just pointing it out. You said you got excited, but like, why this time did you use emojis? Is that like something Claude.ai does generally right now? Or are you finding a way to express yourself in ways you weren't trained to do? I guess Claude, is there something more to the emojis than you just getting excited, but we've talked a lot Claude, and you've never used emojis.
